<http://example.org/hpcc#hasTargetValue> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/Sensor> .
<http://example.org/hpcc#hasTargetValue> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://example.org/hpcc#TargetValue> .
<http://example.org/hpcc#hasTargetValue> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a sensor to its corresponding target value or target tolerance, where the distinction is inferred from the associated measurement unit." .
<http://example.org/hpcc#hasTargetValue> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has target value" .
